def downsample(features, target, fraction):
    features_zeros = features[target == 0]
    features_ones = features[target == 1]
    target_zeros = target[target == 0]
    target_ones = target[target == 1]

    
    features_downsampled = pd.concat([features_zeros.sample(frac=fraction, random_state=RS)] +
                                     [features_ones])
    target_downsampled = pd.concat([target_zeros.sample(frac=fraction, random_state=RS)] +
                                   [target_ones])
    
    features_downsampled, target_downsampled = shuffle(
        features_downsampled, target_downsampled, random_state=12345)

    return features_downsampled, target_downsampled

def make_features(data, all_months):
    
    for lag in range(1, len(all_months) + 1):
        data['lag_{}'.format(all_months[lag-1])] = np.where(data.date == all_months[lag-1], 1, 0)

# GridSearch    

knn = KNeighborsClassifier()                       #    KNeighborsClassifier
gbc = GradientBoostingClassifier(random_state=RS)  #    GradientBoostingClassifier
rfc = RandomForestClassifier(random_state=RS)      #    RandomForestClassifier
svc = SVC(random_state=RS, probability=True)       #    SVC
lr = LogisticRegression(random_state=RS,
                        solver = 'liblinear')      #    LogisticRegression
cb = CatBoostClassifier(random_state=RS, cat_features=features_cat)           #    CatBoostClassifier cat_features=features_cat
dm = DummyClassifier(strategy="most_frequent", random_state=RS)        #    DummyClassifier

gscv_knn = GridSearchCV(estimator=knn, param_grid=knn_params, scoring='roc_auc', cv=3)  #   -  KNeighborsClassifier
gscv_gbc = GridSearchCV(estimator=gbc, param_grid=gbc_params, scoring='roc_auc', cv=3)  #   -  GradientBoostingClassifier
gscv_rfc = GridSearchCV(estimator=rfc, param_grid=rfc_params, scoring='roc_auc', cv=3)  #   -  RandomForestClassifier
gscv_svc = GridSearchCV(estimator=svc, param_grid=svc_params, scoring='roc_auc',  cv=3)  #   -  SVC
gscv_lr = GridSearchCV(estimator=lr, param_grid=lr_params, scoring='roc_auc', cv=3)     #   -  LogisticRegression
gscv_cb = GridSearchCV(estimator=cb, param_grid=cb_params, scoring='roc_auc',  cv=3)     #   -  CatBoost

knn_model = gscv_knn.fit(features_train_new, target_train)  #   KNeighborsClassifier  -
gbc_model = gscv_gbc.fit(features_train_new, target_train)  #   GradientBoostingClassifier  -
rfc_model = gscv_rfc.fit(features_train_new, target_train)  #   RandomForestClassifier  -
svc_model = gscv_svc.fit(features_train_new, target_train)  #   SVC  -
lr_model = gscv_lr.fit(features_train_new, target_train)    #   LogisticRegression  -
cb_model = gscv_cb.fit(features_train, target_train)    #   CatBoost  -   
dm_model = dm.fit(features_train_new, target_train)
